                        </p>

                    </li>
                    <li style="border-bottom:1px solid #989898"><p><a target="_blank" href="http://accountserver.bkinfo.in/news/newsfiles/Cont_Audit_Schedule_1819.png"><text style="color:#F4616B;font-weight:bold">Latest</text><span>Continuous Audit Schedule 2018-19 </span></a></p></li>
                    <li style="border-bottom:1px solid #989898">
                        <p>
                            <b style="color:#25CFAC">Connectone Ver 6.0 Released with following Changes:</b><br />
                            <span>
                                1. Denomination Details added in Collection Box voucher and Collection Box voucher(Printable). There is no  need to create Excel based Collection Box voucher separately<br />
