                                3. Some smaller issues in Accounts Module Fixed<br />
                                4. Various issues fixed in Magazine Module<br />
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="border-bottom:1px solid #989898">
                        <p href="#">
                            <b style="color:#25CFAC">Connectone Version 5.8.2 has been released with following updates:</b><br />
                            <span>
                                Donation in Kind voucher shall automatically post the book value of asset created at Re.1 per Qty mentioned, up to 2 decimal digits. Existing entries in year 1718 shall be updated in Database directly, as per the same mentioned above.
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="border-bottom:1px solid #989898">
                        <p href="#">
                            <b style="color:#25CFAC">Connectone Ver 5.8.1.3 Released with following Changes:</b><br />
                            <span>
                                1. Issue related to last character in GSTN number has been fixed . <br />
                                2. Disabled auto opening of Audit Analysis on Login. To check Audit Analysis , please click `Start-> Account Analysis` <br />
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li style="border-bottom:1px solid #989898">
                        <p href="#">
                            <b style="color:#25CFAC">Connectone Ver 5.8.1 Released with following Changes:</b><br />
                            <span>
                                1. Changed Cash warning message to Rs. 10,000<br />
                                2. Added Cheque printing to Daily Balances Report <br />
                                3. Added GSTIN to Address Book screen <br />
                                4. Magazine module related internal changes<br />
                                5. Sync issue fix<br />
                                6. Added Magazine Related Reports<br />
                                7. Issues related to Update of Payment Voucher related to Construction fixed. <br />
                                8. TDS mapping related restrictions removed <br />
                                9. City related Mandatory check removed in Foreign Donation Screen <br />
                                10. Location related check fixed in Journal Voucher <br />
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div> <!-- notification end -->

        </div><!-- main content middle end -->

